---
title: Flujo de Estados MX (Solicitud de Credito)
---
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> created: create() / status inicial

    created --> fetching_bank_data: update_status()\nworkflow.on_enter -> fetching_bank_data_task
    fetching_bank_data --> validate_country_rules: fetching_bank_data_task\nupdate_status() success
    validate_country_rules --> approved: validate_country_rules_task\nupdate_status() valid=true
    validate_country_rules --> rejected: validate_country_rules_task\nupdate_status() valid=false

    created --> technical_error: bootstrap error
    fetching_bank_data --> technical_error: retries agotados / fallo proveedor
    validate_country_rules --> technical_error: retries agotados / datos faltantes

    approved --> [*]
    rejected --> [*]
    technical_error --> [*]

    note right of created
        Orquestacion state-driven.
        El bootstrap ocurre via update_status().
    end note

    note right of fetching_bank_data
        Guarda BankProviderData antes de transicionar.
        Maneja retry con Celery hasta technical_error.
    end note

    note right of approved
        Estado terminal de negocio.
        workflow.on_enter dispara notify_final_decision_task.
    end note
